item.title: CVE-2024-37283|2024-08-09T15:34:02.839Z -- elastic -- elastic%20agent
item.description: An issue was discovered whereby Elastic Agent will leak secrets from the agent policy elastic-agent.yml only when the log level is configured to debug. By default the log level is set to info, where no leak occurs.
